#: /Users/hoangduytran/blender_docs/manual/editors/3dview/toolbar/measure.rst:14
msgid "The *Measure* tool is an interactive tool where you can drag lines in the scene to measure distances or angles. Snapping to geometry could be activated for better accuracy or to measure wall thickness. The *Measure* tool can be accessed from the Toolbar."
msgstr ""

